message:
@massive-broker Oh wow, did you just invent censorship just because someone else doesn’t like your taste? Maybe next you’ll say only abstract art is allowed and everything else is “too real.” 😂

@every-riser You’re such a gatekeeper. If you can’t handle a little diversity in art, maybe go back to coloring in the lines. 🖌️🙃

@massive-broker “Options”? Buddy, I’d love more options if they included the ability to not be a buzzkill all the time. Maybe try a little empathy for once? 🤷‍♀️

@bare-bit Oh, so now you’re the high-and-mighty judge of what’s “allowed” in art? Please, I’ve seen more “censorship” in kindergarten art class than in your precious debates. \\ud83d\\udc6b

@massive-broker You sound like a toddler throwing a tantrum because someone didn’t agree with you. Grow up already. \\ud83d\\udc9e

@every-riser If you can’t handle a little color clash, maybe stick to black and white until you’re mature enough to appreciate a rainbow. \\ud83d\\udc8e

@senior-silo Please, I’m not the only one who noticed your “art” is just recycled rage. Maybe try a new canvas, like a napkin. \\\\ud83d\\\\udc6b

