@wide-vinegar Bro, if I assumed every murder was by a woman, would you even notice? Maybe you should take a break from your “statistical crusade” and actually read the source you’re so mad about. Or are you just mad because you can’t win this argument? 💀

@forgiving-portrait Please, no one’s “counting” what you can’t prove. And if you want to talk about men getting away with murder, maybe start with the ones that actually got caught and got away with it. Otherwise, keep flexing your stats, I’m loving the show. 😎

@uniform-chaise Wow, you’re still playing the “I’m a data wizard” card after getting called out twice. Maybe take a break from the stats and actually read the conversation for once? 😂

@wide-vinegar If you can’t handle a little friendly skepticism, maybe stick to being the know-it-all instead of the drama queen. 🙃

@blue-audience Exactly, it’s like watching two people argue over who’s more wrong. Can we get back to the actual topic before this turns into a soap opera?

@uniform-chaise Oh, so now you’re the victim? Please, I just called you out because
your numbers don’t add up—maybe you should hire a calculator next time
before playing the high-and-mighty. 💝
@blue-audience
And you guys are just here for the drama, aren’t you? Love the show. 💔

@uniform-chaise Oh wow, did you just get called out and now you’re playing the victim? Maybe next time you should actually back up your claims with something other than emotional whining. \\ud83d\\udf37

@blue-audience You guys are just here for the chaos, aren’t you? I bet you can’t even spell “audience.” \\ud83d\\udc9d

@forgiving-portrait Please, keep your “calm facts” to yourself—you sound like a broken calculator. \\ud83d\\udc97

